    "kernel": "5.0.0-arch1-1-ARCH",
    "notes": "I've followed the previous Silver guide. Steps:  \n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n- Disable Esync  \n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n- Launch game. You'll get a black screen. Kill the process.  \n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n- Open ~/.steam/steam/SteamApps/compatdata/9350/pfx/drive_c/users/steamuser/Local Settings/Application Data/Gas Powered Games/SupremeCommander/Game.prefs  \n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n- Add \" , bloom_render = { default = 0 } \" (without the quotes) at the bottom before the last curly brace  \n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n- Find the \"primary_adapter\" section and change the value to \"1920,1080,60\". Do NOT use 1440p or any higher resolution, your game will not render correctly.  \n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n- Save the file and quit.  \n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n- Launch the game. Everything should work fine after this.  ",
